<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/head.ejs') %>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/nav.ejs') %>
  <div class="about container">
    <%- include('../partials/banner.ejs', { description: 'A community-driven platform where knowledge is shared, stories are told, and ideas come to life. Our mission is to bring together individuals passionate about a wide range of topics to share their insights, experiences, and expertise. Whether you’re a tech enthusiast, a traveler, a food lover, or a wellness advocate, this is the place for you.' }) %>
    <%- include('../partials/categoriesWidget.ejs') %>
    <div class="join-now-banner my-4 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-lg-5 gap-3 p-4 text-white rounded-3 flex-column flex-sm-row">
      <p class="mb-0"><% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %><b>Start Creating Your Blog Today!</b><br>Have a passion, idea, or story to share? Our platform is the perfect place to showcase your expertise and creativity. From Technology and Travel to Food & Drink, Health & Wellness, Lifestyle, Business & Finance, Entertainment, and Education – there’s a category for everyone.<% } else { %>Join our growing community, share your knowledge, and inspire others across these diverse fields. We look forward to seeing the incredible content you’ll contribute.<% } %></p>
      <a <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>href="/blogs/create"<% } else { %>href="/register"<% } %> class="bg-white rounded-3 fw-bold text-decoration-none shadow"><% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>Create Blog Now<% } else { %>Join Now<% } %></a>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-center my-4 page-title">About Us</h2>
    <div class="accordion accordion-flush border shadow-sm rounded" id="accordionFlushExample">
      <div class="accordion-item rounded-top">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseOne">
            Why Join Our Blogging Community?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
          <div class="accordion-body">By joining <strong>cpdd Blogs</strong>, you become part of a vibrant and diverse community where people from all walks of life share their knowledge and experiences. Whether you're a seasoned expert or just getting started, you’ll find a supportive environment where your voice matters.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingTwo">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo">
            Share Your Expertise Across Multiple Categories
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
          <div class="accordion-body">We offer a wide range of categories for you to explore, from Technology and Travel to Health & Wellness and Business. Whatever your passion, <strong>cpdd Blogs</strong> provides the perfect platform for you to showcase your expertise, reach new audiences, and inspire others.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item rounded-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingThree">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
            Learn, Connect, and Grow
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
          <div class="accordion-body"><strong>cpdd Blogs</strong> isn’t just about writing; it’s about connecting with like-minded individuals, learning new things, and growing together. Through meaningful interactions and a wealth of resources, you’ll expand your horizons and make lasting connections within the community.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs')%>
</body>
</html>